divs: sighting detailsonce again strange lights are appearing in the sky around land o lakes, fl (pasco county). lots of streaking lights like falling stars except they streak across the sky rather than falling, sorta like climbing in altitude. (?) then around 2am friday morning oct. 29 i saw a "star" very, very high up sail across the length of the sky until it disappeared. and then saturday 6:15pm (+\-15 min.) a fireball sailed across the eastern sky moving north. things of this nature have occurred off and on since i moved here in jan. of 2008. in the beginning i reported but haven't done so in a long time. but i hope that maybe others in the area might read this and post their sightings in this area too.
Summary: Lights and fire balls Land O Lakes, FL
